notes on getting linux running on a thinkpad w500

the hardware description page is:
http://www-307.ibm.com/pc/support/site.wss/quickPath.do?quickPathEntry=4061A75


After having my usual rant against debian, and wishing i could only had gentoo on this machine, i decided to make 3 partitions out of the 320gig HD.. unfortunately spinning at 5400rpm (the only flaw i can see on the configuration).


